snippet.title: Lisa [RPG Maker]
snippet.description:
I playthrough the RPG Maker game, "Lisa". http://rpgmaker.net/games/4412/

All 3 VHS tapes acquired.

Here's my analysis and review of the game: 
https://zerowiseman.tumblr.com/post/39180106942/lisa-rpg-maker-analysis

Forgive me for getting lost in the white world, I wanted to show all the areas and that area loops.

Made sure to try and show all the areas/text in the game. (didn't manage to get to Rick before using/getting the plastic bag, though.)

Also if the quality is low, sorry. I used livestream's procaster to record this.
